WEBVTT

33:06.870 --> 33:08.270 line:80%
When my father was alive,

33:08.580 --> 33:10.960 line:80%
he often supported
our butcher shop's business.

33:10.960 --> 33:11.960 line:80%
I thought,

33:12.720 --> 33:14.310 line:80%
since Mr. Li is so nice,

33:14.770 --> 33:17.710 line:80%
his manager must be
a wonderful person, too.
